Name: Max Bogue
Date: 5/18/2011

ATTN: If you experiece freezing problems, please press 'n' to hide the
NURB.  It likes to make the scene freeze and crash for me.  Also please
note that there are 6 different patterns used among the cubes.

An awesome 3D scene for CG1.  Developed and built on Mac OS X, but the
makefile supports the following:

    Solaris Build:
      - make
      - make all
      - make tessellation
    OS X Build:
      - make mac
    Cleanup:
      - make clean
      - make realclean
